00:36:30,350 --> 00:36:33,510
It feels like we're the only ones in this world.

524
00:36:33,510 --> 00:36:35,470
You're right.

525
00:36:35,470 --> 00:36:39,120
Inspiration for my new novel is coming to me.

526
00:36:39,120 --> 00:36:41,399
Enough, Damai. Don't be distracted.

527
00:36:41,399 --> 00:36:43,740
Finish the current ending first.

528
00:36:43,740 --> 00:36:45,620
Okay.

529
00:36:47,780 --> 00:36:50,250
Come over and help with setting up the tent!

530
00:36:50,250 --> 00:36:52,360
Coming!

531
00:36:53,670 --> 00:36:55,010
Get to work.

532
00:36:55,010 --> 00:36:56,130
How do we do this?

533
00:36:56,130 --> 00:36:58,669
Hold this. I'll stick the stake into the ground.

534
00:36:58,669 --> 00:37:01,880
Mr. Hu! Why are you slacking off again, Mr. Hu?

535
00:37:01,880 --> 00:37:03,069
Come over and help out.

536
00:37:03,069 --> 00:37:05,420
He's pretending to be deaf.

537
00:37:14,190 --> 00:37:16,749
Mr. Hu, aren't you going to move your hands and help out?

538
00:37:16,749 --> 00:37:21,190
You can't ask an artist to dirty his hands.

539
00:37:21,190 --> 00:37:23,780
Xia Xia! Stop picking wood.

540
00:37:23,780 --> 00:37:25,569
Come here. Have some coffee.

541
00:37:25,569 --> 00:37:28,560
We can always put our faith in Xiao Huang.

542
00:37:28,560 --> 00:37:30,790
I'm not an artist.

543
00:37:32,010 --> 00:37:35,809
I'm elevating your status, but you refuse my kindness.

544
00:37:39,220 --> 00:37:42,300
Let's pick some firewood.

545
00:37:42,300 --> 00:37:45,500
We should gather more. It'll be cold after sunset.

546
00:37:45,500 --> 00:37:47,190
Let's go.

547
00:37:50,050 --> 00:37:51,750
That way.

548
00:38:00,360 --> 00:38:02,670
Pick the thinner ones.

549
00:38:03,510 --> 00:38:05,040
- Yes.
- Okay, those are good.

550
00:38:05,040 --> 00:38:08,260
How I wish I could fall in love.

551
00:38:10,250 --> 00:38:13,239
Don't jump to conclusions. They can't be a couple.

552
00:38:13,239 --> 00:38:15,270
Why not?

553
00:38:15,270 --> 00:38:17,449
They aren't married,

554
00:38:17,449 --> 00:38:20,390
and they're fond of each other.

555
00:38:21,300 --> 00:38:24,550
Hongdou's lease will end next month, right?

556
00:38:24,550 --> 00:38:26,699
Good kids, here's what you don't know.

557
00:38:26,699 --> 00:38:30,010
A time limit...

558
00:38:30,010 --> 00:38:35,690
sparks a brief and passionate love most easily.

559
00:38:39,640 --> 00:38:41,090
Do you agree with him?

560
00:38:41,090 --> 00:38:42,990
Yes, I do.

561
00:38:43,370 --> 00:38:46,420
I'm experienced.

562
00:38:49,050 --> 00:38:53,520
The girl started by saying,

563
00:38:53,520 --> 00:38:55,489
"When you're singing to me,

564
00:38:55,489 --> 00:38:58,510
a special feeling bubbles within me.“

565
00:38:58,510 --> 00:39:00,130
"It's love."

566
00:39:00,130 --> 00:39:03,460
When I just started enjoying the fragrance of love,

567
00:39:03,460 --> 00:39:07,170
she sent me a message and told me

568
00:39:07,170 --> 00:39:08,840
it was all a dream.

569
00:39:08,840 --> 00:39:10,760
I should wake up.

570
00:39:10,760 --> 00:39:12,770
I asked why.

571
00:39:12,770 --> 00:39:14,320
Guess what happened.

572
00:39:14,320 --> 00:39:15,910
What happened?

573
00:39:15,910 --> 00:39:18,350
She blocked me.

574
00:39:19,860 --> 00:39:22,639
The lighting here is good. I'll take a photo for you.

575
00:39:22,639 --> 00:39:27,110
Love comes and goes like a hurricane.

576
00:39:27,110 --> 00:39:29,330
Even though I agree with him,

577
00:39:29,330 --> 00:39:33,099
I think... Hongdou and Chairman Xie are rational people.

578
00:39:33,099 --> 00:39:36,829
They won't begin a relationship they can't be responsible for.

579
00:39:36,829 --> 00:39:41,820
One's reason can stop one from starting a relationship,

580
00:39:41,820 --> 00:39:46,510
but it can't prevent one from developing feelings.

581
00:39:55,960 --> 00:39:58,760
Na Na, what do you think of a story

582
00:39:58,760 --> 00:40:01,149
about a female president going on a trip,

583
00:40:01,150 --> 00:40:02,489
coincidentally meeting an overbearing village beau,

584
00:40:02,490 --> 00:40:05,110
and then help him with his business venture?

585
00:40:05,110 --> 00:40:09,040
♫ <i>Don't know where to go</i> ♫

586
00:40:10,220 --> 00:40:12,810
I can already see the scene in my mind.

587
00:40:14,160 --> 00:40:15,869
Include me in your story.

588
00:40:15,869 --> 00:40:17,770
No way.

589
00:40:17,770 --> 00:40:20,220
Can't I just be a minor character?

590
00:40:20,220 --> 00:40:22,230
Nope.

591
00:40:26,640 --> 00:40:29,499
Come on. Cheers.

592
00:40:29,499 --> 00:40:31,489
- Come on.
- Cheers!

593
00:40:31,489 --> 00:40:33,710
<i>Cheers!</i>

594
00:40:39,740 --> 00:40:41,949
This sweet potato is delicious. It's really sweet.

595
00:40:41,949 --> 00:40:44,079
Lately, everything tastes amazing to me.

596
00:40:44,079 --> 00:40:47,849
Me, too. Aunty Feng's cooking is amazing.

597
00:40:47,849 --> 00:40:52,869
So, people have to work more and put in more effort.

598
00:40:52,869 --> 00:40:57,800
This potato is tastiest with salt and pepper.

599
00:40:58,410 --> 00:41:00,010
It's enough.

600
00:41:05,620 --> 00:41:08,860
Drink less coffee. You won't be able to sleep at night.

601
00:41:08,860 --> 00:41:12,950
I'm not sleeping. I'll stargaze for the whole night.

602
00:41:12,950 --> 00:41:15,730
Do it if you aren't afraid of the cold.

603
00:41:17,410 --> 00:41:22,210
This is wonderful. It's great that we can gather together.

604
00:41:22,210 --> 00:41:24,899
It's a pity! Mr. Ma isn't here!

605
00:41:24,899 --> 00:41:29,080
We'll have everyone with him around, and that's even better!

606
00:41:29,080 --> 00:41:33,330
Damai! When are you leaving?

607
00:41:34,820 --> 00:41:37,110
I'm leaving next week.

608
00:41:37,110 --> 00:41:40,240
I told Xiaochun that I'd check out next week.

609
00:41:40,240 --> 00:41:42,400
Can't you stay for a few more days?

610
00:41:42,400 --> 00:41:43,900
I've been out for too long.

611
00:41:43,900 --> 00:41:47,960
My parents keep calling to ask me to go back.

612
00:41:47,960 --> 00:41:51,400
- Have you told your dad that you won't look for a job?
- Yeah.

613
00:41:51,400 --> 00:41:52,969
I even promised him this.

614
00:41:52,969 --> 00:41:55,770
I'll leave the house at least four days a week.

615
00:41:55,770 --> 00:41:57,320
That's more like it.

616
00:41:57,320 --> 00:42:00,310
Damai, Will you come back and visit us?

617
00:42:00,310 --> 00:42:03,409
Of course. I'll come back and live here again next year.

618
00:42:03,409 --> 00:42:05,780
Will you guys still be around?

619
00:42:05,780 --> 00:42:09,389
I don't know if they'll be around, but I'll definitely be here. I have nowhere else to go.

620
00:42:09,389 --> 00:42:10,738
I'll be here, too.

621
00:42:10,738 --> 00:42:11,759
You have nowhere else to go, too?

622
00:42:11,759 --> 00:42:13,339
That's great.

623
00:42:13,339 --> 00:42:16,119
I'll save a room for you, and give you a discount.

624
00:42:16,119 --> 00:42:19,139
There's no need for that. She can sleep in my room. She doesn't need to pay.

625
00:42:19,200 --> 00:42:25,100
Chairman Xie, you always behave like a shrewd merchant at such moments.

626
00:42:25,160 --> 00:42:26,440
Thank you for your praise.

627
00:42:26,440 --> 00:42:29,240
I'm a proper shrewd merchant, while you pretend to be one.

628
00:42:29,240 --> 00:42:32,609
I heard you only charged ¥200

629
00:42:32,609 --> 00:42:35,010
for Mr. Ma's teahouse love story.

630
00:42:35,010 --> 00:42:36,490
That's just my principle.

631
00:42:36,490 --> 00:42:39,459
I can give friends a discount, but I won't write for free.

632
00:42:39,459 --> 00:42:42,330
I really admire that about you!

633
00:42:45,550 --> 00:42:47,770
Once Damai leaves,

634
00:42:47,770 --> 00:42:51,950
