635
00:42:57,610 --> 00:43:01,709
Dear friend, don't be sad. We're just passing guests at a banquet.

636
00:43:01,709 --> 00:43:05,589
We'll leave once we finish eating, but we'll come again the next day.

637
00:43:05,589 --> 00:43:07,420
That's right.

638
00:43:08,800 --> 00:43:13,139
Mr. Hu, this is the perfect moment for you to grace us with a song.

639
00:43:13,139 --> 00:43:14,760
That's right!

640
00:43:14,760 --> 00:43:16,320
Sure. What do you want to listen to?

641
00:43:16,320 --> 00:43:18,319
I'm not like you guys. I won't charge a cent.

642
00:43:18,319 --> 00:43:20,130
How about "The Price of Love"?

643
00:43:20,130 --> 00:43:23,149
What's the song you sang in your room last night?

644
00:43:23,149 --> 00:43:24,750
It was pretty nice.

645
00:43:24,750 --> 00:43:26,310
That's my new song.

646
00:43:26,310 --> 00:43:28,410
Sing that.

647
00:43:30,740 --> 00:43:34,120
My new song, "Wind." Please enjoy.

